== 预算 ==
[[File:NASA-Budget-Federal.svg|thumb]]
在1966年[[阿波罗计划|阿波罗计划]]期间，NASA在联邦总预算中的份额达到顶峰，约为4.41%。在1975年迅速下降到约1%，并保持在该水平附近，直到1998年<ref name=":00">{{Cite news |url=http://www.ozy.com/2016/your-presidential-candidates-for-the-milky-way/69557 |title=Your Presidential Candidates ... For the Milky Way |last=Fouriezos |first=Nick |date=2016-05-30 |website=OZY |access-date=2016-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530225641/http://www.ozy.com/2016/your-presidential-candidates-for-the-milky-way/69557 |archive-date=2016-05-30 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>Rogers, Simon. (2010-02-01) [https://www.theguardian.com/news/datablog/2010/feb/01/nasa-budgets-us-spending-space-travel Nasa budgets: US spending on space travel since 1958 |Society] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170131121226/https://www.theguardian.com/news/datablog/2010/feb/01/nasa-budgets-us-spending-space-travel |date=2017-01-31}}. theguardian.com. Retrieved on 2013-08-26.</ref>。然后比例逐渐下降，直到2006年再次持平，约为半数（在2012年估计为0.48%）<ref name="B2013">{{cite web |url=https://www.nasa.gov/pdf/622643main_FY%2013%20Budget%20Presentation.pdf |title=Fiscal Year 2013 Budget Estimates |publisher=NASA |access-date=2013-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023175740/http://www.nasa.gov/pdf/622643main_FY%2013%20Budget%20Presentation.pdf |archive-date=2012-10-23 |url-status=live}}</ref>。在2012年3月[[美国参议院商务、科学和交通委员会|美国参议院科学委员会]]的一次听证会上，[[科技传播学|科学传播者]][[奈爾·德葛拉司·泰森|奈爾·德葛拉司·泰森]]作证说：「现在，美国航空航天局的年度预算是你税收的半分钱。只要两倍——「一美元上的一分钱」——我们就能把这个国家从一个对经济斗争感到厌倦闷闷不乐的国家，转变为一个重新获得20世纪与生俱来明日梦想的国家。」<ref name="tysontranscript">{{cite web |url=http://www.haydenplanetarium.org/tyson/read/2012/03/07/past-present-and-future-of-nasa-us-senate-testimony |title=Past, Present, and Future of NASA — U.S. Senate Testimony |publisher=Hayden Planetarium |date=2012-03-07 |access-date=2012-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121029100131/http://www.haydenplanetarium.org/tyson/read/2012/03/07/past-present-and-future-of-nasa-us-senate-testimony |archive-date=2012-10-29 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="tysontranscript_video">{{cite web |url=http://www.haydenplanetarium.org/tyson/watch/2012/03/07/past-present-and-future-of-nasa-us-senate-testimony-video |title=Past, Present, and Future of NASA — U.S. Senate Testimony (Video) |publisher=Hayden Planetarium |date=2012-03-07 |access-date=2012-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130115121333/http://www.haydenplanetarium.org/tyson/watch/2012/03/07/past-present-and-future-of-nasa-us-senate-testimony-video |archive-date=2013-01-15 |url-status=live}}</ref>

